BudgetSMS,net,is,an,SMS,service,that,can,often,provide,many,routes,to,a,single,destination,and,handle,a,large,volume,of,messages,Their,messaging,gateway,can,send,SMS,to,almost,any,network,in,the,world,The,BudgetSMS,net,API,allows,users,to,send,SMS,messages,check,their,credit,balances,and,get,information,on,a,mobile,phone,operator